          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-8-1647971415602-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the lean beef mince is cooking, add your <strong>spaghetti</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>spaghetti </strong>for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite, then drain and return to the pot until serving</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> beef stock mix </strong>and <strong>soy sauce</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-10-1647971431936-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-10-1647971431936-x400.jpg",
