            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> lean beef bolognese</strong> over the<strong> spaghetti</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and enjoy!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Loved this recipe? Us too! That’s why it’s one of our Everyday Favourites, available every week.</span></strong></p>",
